<br>
It is up to each generation to sustain that original vision, and see to it that the conditions of each time do not so distort that vision as to make it unrecognizable.<br>
<br>
This is our acknowledgement of sacrifices that have been made before us to achieve what America was, as founded.  It is also our trust and responsibilty to the future generations of Americans.<br>
<br>
Our fight here is an example of a demand for rational government.<br>
<br>
I recall the words of the President in the movie Independence Day, &quot;we will not go quietly into that dark night, we will not give up without a fight&quot;.<br>
<br>
Sustain the vision, continue to do your part.  We can and do make a difference.  To think otherwise is to promulgate a despicable lie.<br>
<br>
We are better than that.  America is better than that. <br>
<br>
That is MY stand!<br>
